oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: L.A.M.F. at Exit-In
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:subject: Split fountain printing; Woodcuts (prints);
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: One color window card (split fountain, orange to green, on white) announcing L.A.M.F. at the Exit-In in Nashville, Tennessee on July 16. Poster features a woodcut of a man smoking a pipe.
